.el .ds Aq '
.TH tapectl 1  "tapectl 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
tapectl \- Multi\-tenant archival storage management for LTO tape and exportable encrypted directories
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtapectl\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-y\fR|\fB\-\-yes\fR] [\fB\-\-config\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Multi\-tenant archival storage management for LTO tape and exportable encrypted directories
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be done without making changes
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose output
.TP
\fB\-y\fR, \fB\-\-yes\fR
Skip confirmation prompts
.TP
\fB\-\-config\fR \fI<CONFIG>\fR
Path to config file
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
tapectl\-init(1)
Initialize tapectl (DB, config, operator tenant, keys)
.TP
tapectl\-tenant(1)
Manage tenants
.TP
tapectl\-key(1)
Manage encryption keys
.TP
tapectl\-unit(1)
Manage archival units
.TP
tapectl\-snapshot(1)
Manage snapshots
.TP
tapectl\-stage(1)
Stage snapshots for writing
.TP
tapectl\-staging(1)
Manage staging area
.TP
tapectl\-volume(1)
Manage volumes and tape operations
.TP
tapectl\-cartridge(1)
Manage physical cartridges
.TP
tapectl\-archive\-set(1)
Manage archive set policies
.TP
tapectl\-audit(1)
Policy compliance audit
.TP
tapectl\-catalog(1)
Browse and search file catalog
.TP
tapectl\-location(1)
Manage storage locations
.TP
tapectl\-report(1)
Generate reports
.TP
tapectl\-restore(1)
Restore data from volumes
.TP
tapectl\-export(1)
Export encrypted slices to directory
.TP
tapectl\-import(1)
Import a pre\-existing volume into the database
.TP
tapectl\-quick\-archive(1)
Quick archive: create + stage + write in one flow
.TP
tapectl\-db(1)
Database operations
.TP
tapectl\-config(1)
Configuration management
.TP
tapectl\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
.TP
tapectl\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
